# Force LF line endings for all text files everywhere — the repo, your local
# clone's working tree, and the Linux GitHub Actions build all agree on LF.
# This stops the OneDrive -> clone sync (sync-to-repo.bat) from showing
# "changed" files that differ only by line endings (CRLF vs LF).
* text=auto eol=lf
 
# Binary files: never translate their bytes.
*.png  binary
*.jpg  binary
*.jpeg binary
*.gif  binary
*.pdf  binary
*.ico  binary
 
